superpowers-ml
==============

This project is a fork of Superpowers (https://github.com/obra/superpowers),
created by Jesse Vincent <jesse@fsck.com> and licensed under the MIT License.

All original Superpowers content is retained unchanged except where explicitly
noted. This fork adds a conservative machine-learning research layer:

  - "## ML research addendum" sections appended to five existing skills:
    brainstorming, writing-plans, test-driven-development, systematic-debugging,
    and verification-before-completion. Original skill text is unchanged above
    each addendum.

  - three new skills: ml-experiment-design, ml-feedback-ladder, ml-result-review.

  - docs/superpowers-ml.md, describing the ML layer and the R0-R7 verification
    rungs.

The original copyright and MIT license terms are retained in full. See LICENSE.
